{"tid":109140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點先係荃灣搵返男朋友呀","createTime":"2017-02-05T18:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T19:31:06.000Z","uid":65656,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5208e2a898ae43d0c39dd284e4d4b87fed9d0e0","tid":109140,"uid":65656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂 同男朋友嘈交，佢話出黎搵我，<br />\n我又未同佢講自己係邊既時候佢電話就冇電啦！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n荃灣咁大點搵到佢呀 戇居居企左係到驚佢搵我唔到 嗚呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8073ef4dc8c72e897ecd4a24e4d733883253bc","tid":109140,"uid":9185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:13:17.000Z","msg":"小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識搵電話打俾你/去7仔租尿袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"f755017701537470978c37a207a68b698669633e","tid":109140,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:13:21.000Z","msg":"問人借電話打俾人尸"},{"pid":"dc53910468f39cd92bb4a2fc54f73dbf932f18b5","tid":109140,"uid":65656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識搵電話打俾你/去7仔租尿袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n屌屌我都係想知點解佢唔借人電話打比我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a8ccaefaaeb0de10a8d0585b2ee58b9bdbd4a4","tid":109140,"uid":65656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問人借電話打俾人尸</blockquote><br />\n係佢電話冇電我搵佢唔到 好撚凍呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"